1
00:00:00,499 --> 00:00:05,023
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

2
00:00:05,023 --> 00:00:10,527
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

3
00:00:10,527 --> 00:00:16,955
♪I really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster♪

4
00:00:16,955 --> 00:00:21,435
♪Can I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more♪

5
00:00:21,435 --> 00:00:25,883
♪Holding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journey♪

6
00:00:25,883 --> 00:00:30,794
♪The chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after another♪

7
00:00:30,794 --> 00:00:34,843
♪The promised moment
will definitely not be forgotten♪

8
00:00:34,843 --> 00:00:39,378
♪Can I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat♪

9
00:00:39,378 --> 00:00:43,675
♪Start the countdown 4321,
a new scenery♪

10
00:00:43,675 --> 00:00:48,440
♪I want to see all the scenes about you♪

11
00:00:48,440 --> 00:00:51,931
♪No need to miss you anymore♪

12
00:00:51,931 --> 00:00:55,611
♪Right by your side♪

13
00:00:57,257 --> 00:01:00,635
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,635 --> 00:01:03,008
=Episode 15=

15
00:01:03,466 --> 00:01:04,800
I have a scoop for you.

16
00:01:05,633 --> 00:01:06,233
What is it?

17
00:01:06,233 --> 00:01:08,466
Miss Jin has a little sister.

18
00:01:16,100 --> 00:01:17,633
It's about to start soon.

19
00:01:17,700 --> 00:01:19,333
Why hasn't Lan Chen shown up yet?

20
00:01:19,966 --> 00:01:21,504
Did he chicken out?

21
00:01:25,133 --> 00:01:26,299
Miss Jin.

22
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:27,933
Miss Jin, could you explain?

23
00:01:30,500 --> 00:01:33,800
Regarding the recent events,

24
00:01:33,966 --> 00:01:35,799
I'm here to explain it.

25
00:01:35,899 --> 00:01:36,799
So, is that true?

26
00:01:36,900 --> 00:01:37,966
Is Lan Chen behind that?

27
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:40,166
Is it him?

28
00:01:40,233 --> 00:01:40,699
I will...

29
00:01:40,700 --> 00:01:41,466
Miss Jin.

30
00:01:44,833 --> 00:01:46,333
Didn't I give you a day off?

31
00:01:49,700 --> 00:01:50,900
I should be responsible

32
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:52,566
for what I did.

33
00:01:55,066 --> 00:01:55,968
It's the time.

34
00:01:56,833 --> 00:02:00,672
We will issue a statement on this event.

35
00:02:01,399 --> 00:02:02,466
Everyone, please sit.

36
00:02:03,166 --> 00:02:06,566
Let Miss Jin finish.

37
00:02:06,766 --> 00:02:09,184
If any media present do not cooperate,

38
00:02:10,500 --> 00:02:11,766
I would get them out.

39
00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:28,320
(Press Conference)

40
00:02:36,233 --> 00:02:38,999
Thank you all for coming.

41
00:02:39,700 --> 00:02:43,066
We are truly sorry

42
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:44,666
for negative influence yesterday.

43
00:02:45,100 --> 00:02:47,566
So, we're holding a press conference

44
00:02:47,633 --> 00:02:49,666
to make a formal statement to everyone.

45
00:02:50,066 --> 00:02:56,866
Recently, regarding the attack
on WE Beauty Family's CFO Zuo Jiazhang

46
00:02:57,033 --> 00:03:01,133
and creative director Mei Xiangfa,

47
00:03:01,200 --> 00:03:06,166
it has been confirmed
that it was Jin Xi'en's individual act.

48
00:03:06,656 --> 00:03:09,366
It has nothing to do
with the WE Beauty Family.

49
00:03:09,633 --> 00:03:11,766
After deliberation,

50
00:03:12,366 --> 00:03:14,966
the group has dismissed Jin Xi'en

51
00:03:15,466 --> 00:03:19,699
and reserves the right
to pursue all relevant responsibilities.

52
00:03:21,632 --> 00:03:25,600
This concerns the image of the group,
and it is a critical moment now.

53
00:03:25,833 --> 00:03:30,112
Being lenient will lead to a disaster.

54
00:03:30,784 --> 00:03:32,199
I will do as grandfather said.

55
00:03:34,766 --> 00:03:38,624
Good for you.

56
00:03:39,456 --> 00:03:41,333
Men should see the bigger picture.

57
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:46,699
WE Group should be responsible

58
00:03:46,833 --> 00:03:48,999
for Jin Xi'en's improper actions.

59
00:03:49,033 --> 00:03:51,933
We will improve our recruitment system.

60
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:09,088
All this has nothing to do
with Miss Jin.

61
00:04:10,272 --> 00:04:11,456
I'm behind this.

62
00:04:12,566 --> 00:04:14,400
I will take all responsibility.

63
00:04:16,300 --> 00:04:21,536
Also, if any media slanders Miss Jin
and her family,

64
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:24,992
I will make them pay.

65
00:04:31,936 --> 00:04:34,200
Okay, that's all. Stop shooting.

66
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:36,500
We suspend the press conference.

67
00:04:36,928 --> 00:04:38,944
(WE Beauty Family Press Conference)

68
00:04:44,700 --> 00:04:47,466
Mrs. Lan, could you further explain it?

69
00:04:57,100 --> 00:04:59,040
As the company's president,

70
00:04:59,733 --> 00:05:02,720
he has the final say.

71
00:05:03,566 --> 00:05:05,333
We will support him.

72
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:08,736
(Yes, it's Lan Chen.)

73
00:05:13,866 --> 00:05:15,904
(Lan Chen as you know.)

74
00:05:16,666 --> 00:05:18,099
(Since he took office as president,)

75
00:05:18,266 --> 00:05:21,966
(he has always managed the company
in a threatening and autocratic way.)

76
00:05:22,900 --> 00:05:25,333
(I am Zuo Jiazhang, the group's CFO.)

77
00:05:25,366 --> 00:05:26,599
(Without the president's permission,)

78
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:29,333
(how dare I cook the books
in the company?)

79
00:05:29,366 --> 00:05:30,333
What's going on?

80
00:05:33,366 --> 00:05:36,266
(I am Mei Xiangfa,
the group's creative director.)

81
00:05:36,400 --> 00:05:39,233
(It's Lan Chen's fault.)

82
00:05:39,266 --> 00:05:41,199
(Because of his reckless behavior,)

83
00:05:41,233 --> 00:05:44,799
(the company failed
to cooperate with Lihuai International.)

84
00:05:44,866 --> 00:05:47,499
(It's all because of him.)

85
00:05:51,033 --> 00:05:52,999
(He has always managed the company)

86
00:05:53,066 --> 00:05:57,760
(in an autocratic and threatening way.)

87
00:05:58,666 --> 00:06:01,566
(Externally, he monopolizes the market.)

88
00:06:02,466 --> 00:06:04,832
(And he even wants to...)

89
00:06:05,966 --> 00:06:09,399
(Only by replacing Lan Chen
can the company become better)

90
00:06:09,466 --> 00:06:11,552
(and prevent an autocratic system.)

91
00:06:11,552 --> 00:06:12,768
Turn off the video.

92
00:06:19,533 --> 00:06:22,099
Please respond to it.

93
00:06:22,166 --> 00:06:24,700
Please, Mr. Lan.

94
00:06:24,766 --> 00:06:27,966
Mr. Lan, please explain.

95
00:06:39,060 --> 00:06:43,582
♪I pass through the crowd with you♪

96
00:06:46,612 --> 00:06:51,573
♪As if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other♪

97
00:06:54,622 --> 00:07:00,446
♪When the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps in♪

98
00:07:00,446 --> 00:07:06,912
♪You come with light,
shining into my heart♪

99
00:07:07,584 --> 00:07:11,397
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

100
00:07:11,397 --> 00:07:15,518
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

101
00:07:15,518 --> 00:07:17,214
♪Open my secret♪

102
00:07:17,214 --> 00:07:23,262
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

103
00:07:23,262 --> 00:07:27,134
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

104
00:07:27,134 --> 00:07:31,640
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

105
00:07:33,632 --> 00:07:40,350
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪
